import React from 'react' import styles from './EconomyNewsFeedList.module.css' function EconomyNewsFeedList(props) { return (
    {props.feeds.map((feeds) => (

    {feeds.title}

    {feeds.content}

    Read More

    Source: {feeds.source}

    {feeds.time}

    ))}
) } export default EconomyNewsFeedList
